Metadata: Hui Mālama Loko Iʻa Gathering February 6-9, 2020
Indigenous Aquaculture Collaborative First Summit Meeting entitled: Hui Malala Lolo I’a Gathering 2020, February 6-9, 2020, Oahu, Hawaii

Washington Sea Grant introduced members of the Indigenous Aquaculture Collaborative with a slide presentation introducing each participating member. Through this presentation they share their voices for the first time at the Collaborative’s first summit meeting entitled Hui Malala Lolo I’a on February 6, 2020.
